...but we aren't
always meant to know

285
00:22:54,451 --> 00:22:56,522
why things happen
the way they do.

286
00:22:57,041 --> 00:22:59,242
Sometimes, we just
have to accept it...

287
00:22:59,442 --> 00:23:01,202
...as God's will.

288
