Hey, Kent. You were right.

325
00:26:38,656 --> 00:26:40,486
Screw Drumlin.
We'll raise the money

326
00:26:40,487 --> 00:26:42,217
ourselves. We'll
go to New Mexico.

327
00:26:42,457 --> 00:26:44,656
