me know how it goes.

328
00:26:44,896 --> 00:26:47,694
I've got more corporate stops
on the East Coast for you.

329
00:26:47,895 --> 00:26:50,896
Did that investor from
Houston ever get back to us?

330
00:26:51,056 --> 00:26:52,975
I'll hit him up
on my way to L.A.

331
