They've been making money
off aliens for years.

333
00:26:59,015 --> 00:27:01,534
- Begging is good for the soul.
- We'll see.

334
00:27:01,894 --> 00:27:03,454
Just do me a favor.

335
00:27:03,813 --> 00:27:06,173
Try not to be too...
confrontational.

336
00:27:06,654 --> 00:27:08,853
Confrontational?
Me? What do you mean?

337
00:27:09,053 --> 00:27:10,613
I'll see if I left anything.

338
00:27:42,569 --> 00:27:44,382
It's a unique time
in our history,

339
00:27:44,383 --> 00:27:46,249
in the history of
any civilization.

340
00:27:46,409 --> 00:27:49,088
It's the moment of the
acquisition of technology.

341
00:27:49,249 --> 00:27:52,007
That's the moment where
contact becomes possible.

342
00:27:52,767 --> 00:27:54,927
The Very Large Array
in New Mexico...

343
00:27:55,168 --> 00:27:57,328
...is the key to our
chances for success.

344
