With its 27 linked
radio telescopes...

345
00:27:59,767 --> 00:28:01,607
...we can search
more accurately

346
00:28:01,608 --> 00:28:03,167
than at any other facility.

347
00:28:03,327 --> 00:28:05,489
We've gotten
approval to buy the

348
00:28:05,490 --> 00:28:07,846
telescope time
from the government.

349
00:28:08,686 --> 00:28:10,766
Now all we really
need is the money.

350
00:28:11,486 --> 00:28:13,406
A nice presentation, Doctor.

351
00:28:14,085 --> 00:28:16,964
But while our foundation arm
has a mandate to support...

352
