00:30:42,590 --> 00:30:44,509
...of that
son-of-a-bitch!

385
00:30:56,427 --> 00:30:58,306
Welcome back, Dr. C.

386
00:30:58,547 --> 00:30:59,987
How'd it go?

387
00:31:00,627 --> 00:31:02,147
How was the trip?

388
00:31:02,386 --> 00:31:03,746
I've had better.

389
00:31:04,346 --> 00:31:07,267
Drumlin! Is this a
personal vendetta now?

