There's been enormous pressure
from other scientists as well.

391
00:31:11,385 --> 00:31:14,384
It doesn't matter. Hadden's
funding us for 2 more years.

392
00:31:14,586 --> 00:31:16,543
The government
doesn't want their

393
00:31:16,544 --> 00:31:18,905
telescopes used by
the high priestess...

394
