What?

396
00:31:23,384 --> 00:31:26,584
Staring at TV static for hours,
listening to washing machines.

397
00:31:26,823 --> 00:31:28,743
These stories get out!

398
00:31:28,943 --> 00:31:30,544
I was seeking
patterns in the chaos!

399
00:31:30,704 --> 00:31:32,704
It doesn't matter,
we're a joke to them.

400
00:31:32,904 --> 00:31:34,223
They want us out!

401
00:31:35,943 --> 00:31:38,703
We've got 3 months till
the paperwork goes through.

402
00:31:42,382 --> 00:31:44,461
I'll start looking
for other funding.

403
00:31:44,981 --> 00:31:48,581
Could you face reality?
Just this once? We lost.

404
00:31:49,300 --> 00:31:50,541
It's over.

405
00:31:56,940 --> 00:31:58,059
Fine.

406
00:31:58,700 --> 00:32:00,219
I'm not stopping.

407
00:32:00,779 --> 00:32:03,740
If I have to, I'll go it
alone. I've done it before.

