bestseller list.

415
00:33:09,251 --> 00:33:12,091
Thanks for being here.
You've had quite a ride...

416
00:33:12,291 --> 00:33:13,731
...the last few years.

417
00:33:13,891 --> 00:33:15,531
Yeah, I sure have, Larry.

418
