I'm asking is this:

426
00:33:39,968 --> 00:33:41,368
Are we happier...

427
00:33:42,008 --> 00:33:43,714
...as a human
race? Is the world

428
00:33:43,715 --> 00:33:45,367
fundamentally a better place...

429
00:33:45,567 --> 00:33:47,488
...because of science
and technology?

430
00:33:48,128 --> 00:33:50,488
