synthesized society...

435
00:34:01,046 --> 00:34:03,126
...in a hurry to get to the...

436
00:34:17,243 --> 00:34:18,845
We're looking for the meaning.

437
00:34:19,163 --> 00:34:20,403
What is the meaning?

438
00:34:20,564 --> 00:34:23,203
We have mindless jobs,
take frantic vacations.

439
00:34:23,603 --> 00:34:26,442
Deficit finance trips to
the mall to buy things...

440
00:34:26,684 --> 00:34:30,083
...that we think will fill
these holes in our lives.

